  "content": {
    "policiesHeader": "We, at HackMTY, process your provided information in order to organize the best possible hackathon. This may also include images and videos featuring you during the event. Your data will be preliminarily used for admissions, and any images or videos may be used for marketing and archiving. For more information on the processing of your personal data and on how to exercise your rights of access, rectification, suppression, limitation, portability and opposition please visit our Privacy and Cookies Policy."
